title: Result Oriented
text: Completed the assigned engagement deliverables as outlined in the deliverables section.

title: Adaptable
text: Readily accepted changing priorities, was open to new ideas and/or approaches, was willing to take on new responsibilities and proactively adjusted plans to meet changing needs.

title: Customer Focused
text: Was committed to meeting or exceeding customer satisfaction by; accurately scoping work and ensuring agreed to commitments were met (provided quality work in a timely, cost effective manner).

title: Team Player
text: Worked collaboratively, willingly shared information and expertise, and put customer and team needs ahead of oneself.

title: Opportunistic
text: Proactively identified and solved customer problems, understood and considered the broader, big picture impact of decisions.
